latestPosts.caption:
Luxurious photo session in the style of @maisonmargiela ! ✨

It was a real performance, the shots and the role of the model on this shooting took my breath away. ✨

I felt one with art, along with a talented friend @lukanvol who, like a real model, posed as for a glossy @vogue . 

The talented, young photographer @zvichayno demonstrated his professionalism in these shots, that’s wow!✨

Gorgeous makeup artist: @_sofia.lap_ 
Assistant: @rmttkv 
Video: @llevchykk 

It’s fantastic, thank you guys ✨🖤
